wn18rr = load_wn18rr()

    ['train'][:, (2)]))
ent_valid = np.union1d(np.unique(wn18rr['valid'][:, (0)]), np.unique(wn18rr
    ['valid'][:, (2)]))
ent_test = np.union1d(np.unique(wn18rr['test'][:, (0)]), np.unique(wn18rr[
    'test'][:, (2)]))
distinct_ent = np.union1d(np.union1d(ent_train, ent_valid), ent_test)
distinct_rel = np.union1d(np.union1d(np.unique(wn18rr['train'][:, (1)]), np
    .unique(wn18rr['train'][:, (1)])), np.unique(wn18rr['train'][:, (1)]))
